    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " It is supposed, where there is that accord with God, that what was last, and is next after, said implies, there will be no disposition to ask any thing disagreeable to his will, or otherwise than as he hath expressed his will about the matter of prayer. And then, ",
